"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932509-Adam-Peaty-Team-GB-2024-Olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Adam Peaty wants swimming stars to be guaranteed prize money when they compete in theOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 96, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In April this year, World Athletics announcedthat winning a medal in Paris would mean a financial reward, and Peaty now wants his own sport to follow suit.\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9984692502088236, \"rank\": 0.001533096578408577, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 166, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999989051958, \"rank\": 1.0947463895276714e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty, 29, has won two silver medals in France, finishing second in both the 100m breaststroke and 4x100m relay medley.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8501604862058423, \"rank\": 0.16819469336400758, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's taken his overall Olympic medal tally to six, despitetesting positive for Covid-19during the Games.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But now Peaty has called for swimming to fall in line with other authorities.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's got to.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think the IOC has to give back more to the athletes now,\\\" he toldinews.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1438659804102466e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And so they should.\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are the entertainment.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think a phone (Samsung have provided every athlete at the Games with a new phone) and the Village is enough - and the athletes are waking up to that.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 721, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9996722342572281, \"rank\": 0.00032764953686642486, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But that's a very complex question with very complex answers, because I know the governing bodies are funding that at the moment.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But World Aquatics has more than enough money to go around.\\\"\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999989051958, \"rank\": 1.0947463895276714e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9986395798470692, \"rank\": 0.0013622733048114298, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To supplement his own income, the icon runs the Adam Peaty Sports Clinic as well as the AP Race Club, offering advice and guidance to swimmers.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999997458894864, \"rank\": 2.1947170446171025e-07, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he also cited the gruelling swimming schedule as further reason to reward competitors.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The last 14 months have been relentless, the sacrifices I have had to make,\\\" he continued, before refusing to commit to the Summer Games in Los Angeles in 2028.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1704, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999825029137, \"rank\": 1.1074380543063682e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's also not important to know that right now.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the most important thing is that we relax, have a nice bottle of wine, steak, some good food at home and just do something normal.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Go for a walk and enjoy that normality.\\\"\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Olympic silver medallist wins appeal after disqualification for nudging opponent  Do not miss:BBC's Jessica Ennis-Hill in tears as she makes heartbreaking family confession  Do not miss:Team GB star slams athlete's village standards as rival taken to hospital  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9864239125934371, \"rank\": 0.013197760228354755, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/